Package wei.task

Class TaskManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • wei.task.TaskManager
  • public class TaskManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the Task Manager which maintains a list of Task, it provides some functions to manipulate the task list, e.g. add a new task, print the task list, update a task, remove a task, etc.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Wei Wang

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      TaskManager()
      Constructor for objects of class TaskManager, initialize an empty list of task.
